# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` for local development with `npm run dev`.
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored — never commit real secret values.
#
# Generate a strong WEBHOOK_SECRET with:  openssl rand -hex 32
# This same value must be set as a secret on the Pages project AND configured
# on uazapi as the `x-webhook-token` header. See docs/env-vars.md.

# --- Required: shared secret for the webhook + inspector API ---
WEBHOOK_SECRET=replace-me-with-a-long-random-string

# --- Optional (Meta CAPI). Leave unset for capture-only mode. ---
# With these unset, CTWA events are still captured to D1; the Lead just lands
# as lead_status='skipped_no_creds' instead of being sent to Meta.
# See docs/meta-capi-setup.md for how to obtain each value.
# META_DATASET_ID=
# META_CAPI_TOKEN=
# META_PAGE_ID=
# META_TEST_EVENT_CODE=
# META_CURRENCY=BRL
# META_LEAD_EVENT_NAME=LeadSubmitted
# META_PURCHASE_EVENT_NAME=Purchase

# --- Website funnel: LP /topazio + dashboard /dashboard ---
# DASH_KEY gates the dashboard and the read API (/api/leads) AND the
# QualifiedLead write (/api/fire-qualified-lead-web). Use a long random string.
# DASH_KEY=replace-me-with-a-long-random-string
#
# Website Pixel + Conversions API (used by functions/tracker.js for the LP form
# `Lead`/`PageView`, and by /api/fire-qualified-lead-web for the manual
# `QualifiedLead`). These are the *website* dataset creds (Pixel ID + an access
# token with ads_management/business_management). Distinct from META_DATASET_ID/
# META_CAPI_TOKEN above, which power the CTWA business_messaging path.
# Also paste YOUR_META_PIXEL_ID into topazio/index.html (fbq init).
# META_PIXEL_ID=
# META_ACCESS_TOKEN=
# META_QUALIFIED_LEAD_EVENT_NAME=QualifiedLead
# DEFAULT_COUNTRY_CODE=55
#
# Per-page Pixel routing (página B = /topaziob, público distinto, Pixel próprio).
# O navegador da B usa o Pixel hardcoded em topaziob/index.html (1096376869378409);
# estas envs fazem o CAPI server-side mandar os eventos page:'B' para o MESMO Pixel.
# Se ficarem vazias, a B cai no Pixel/token da página A.
# META_PIXEL_ID_B=
# META_ACCESS_TOKEN_B=
#
# Optional GA4 server-side (Measurement Protocol). Leave unset to skip GA4.
# Página A:
# GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-2QH3VL6WB1
# GA4_API_SECRET=
# Página B (/topaziob) — propriedade GA4 própria:
# GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID_B=G-X23KV38189
# GA4_API_SECRET_B=
